Your presence makes a group stronger than the sum of its parts. Pay ''1x Leadership'' and narrate an order to the group, any //Support// or //Assistance// in carrying out that order is considered //Collaboration// (i.e. $$+s$$), including help generated by other talents (e.g. [[♣ Heads Up!]]).